div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><h2 class="comments-title"> 1 comment</h2><ol class="commentlist"><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-18443"> <article id="comment-18443" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/87fb3971eeb2e802616e429b2f2badd5?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">simona</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/09/il-ritorno-del-barbiere-di-siviglia-al-teatro-massimo-di-palermo/#comment-18443"><time datetime="2013-09-21T08:48:28+00:00">21 settembre 2013 at 08:48</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>Che peccato nn essere in Sicilia per vederlo&#8230; complimenti al direttore Stefano Montanari</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li></ol><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2013/09/il-ritorno-del-barbiere-di-siviglia-al-teatro-massimo-di-palermo/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sarà pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="required">*</span></p><p class="comment-form-comment"><label for="comment">Commento</label><textarea id="comment" name="comment" cols="45" rows="8" maxlength="65525" aria-required="true" required="required"></textarea></p><p class="comment-form-author"><label for="author">Nome <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="author" name